00:38:53.440 --> 00:38:55.800
that I've parked out in long-term memory.

00:38:55.800 --> 00:38:59.200
I'll grab that, pull that
into my working memory,

00:38:59.200 --> 00:39:01.410
and oh, yes, while I'm doing that,

00:39:01.410 --> 00:39:04.610
my other arms of my
attentional octopus are free

