00:39:52.215 --> 00:39:55.590
from normal, non-experts by the fact

00:39:55.590 --> 00:39:59.660
that they have all sorts
of sets of neural links

00:39:59.660 --> 00:40:02.409
that they've created and
parked in long-term memory,

00:40:02.409 --> 00:40:05.070
and they can access 'em and bring 'em

00:40:05.070 --> 00:40:07.480
up into working memory
