and so, really, the important,

00:41:12.810 --> 00:41:15.400
a really important part of learning

00:41:15.400 --> 00:41:20.400
is creating these nice sets
of long-term memory links

00:41:21.389 --> 00:41:23.655
that you can just instantly
pull into working memory

00:41:23.655 --> 00:41:25.870
whenever you need to.

